      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>The African Female Initiative is a Non-Governmental organization that seeks to practically empower African females through advocacy, literacy, and education. We create sustainable change by helping African females at every stage of their life. Our goal is to produce educated young women with leadership potential, prepared to overcome unique challenges in academia, health, career, and entrepreneurship.</p>
