      <h2>Our Mission & Vision</h2>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <h3>Mission</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>To increase literacy rates in the African girl child population by providing resources.</li>
            <li>To provide mentorship for bright young girls to further their educational journey.</li>
            <li>To provide development skills for bright young girls positioning them for business, industry, and leadership.</li>
            <li>To educate young girls on reproductive health and general wellbeing.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <h3>Vision</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Contribute to SDG 4 and 5 (quality education and gender equality).</li>
            <li>Build a community of empowered young female thought leaders and change-makers.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
