          <p>Partnered with Yemiyiefo Foundation Ghana to support Ewurama's education journey by providing study materials and personal upkeep.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
          <h3>Menstrual Hygiene Day Workshop</h3>
          <p>Organized a workshop for 50 girls on menstrual hygiene, led by Dr. Stacey Asante-Asamani, including interactive activities and donations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
          <h3>Book and Career Fair</h3>
          <p>Our fair focused on career guidance through inspiring expert speakers and networking opportunities, attended by over 150 girls from Nkanfoa Community.</p>
